headline: My 3 Favorite Stocks to Buy Right Now
summary: Roku is a long-term growth play with recent volatility and a promising ad partnership with Amazon.  Costco continues to deliver market-beating returns, justifying its premium price tag.  Target is a risky turnaround story, priced for pessimism but showing signs of a strategic comeback.
